metadata.name: Jungle Environment Sweater
metadata.description:
We are delighted to announce that all proceeds generated from this auction will be donated to support this vital cause.

Through this auction, we hope to engage a broad audience and inspire them to take meaningful steps for the conservation and protection of our precious jungles.

In addition to participating in the auction through direct bidding, we provide another way to participate. By creating and sharing a unique referral link, you can earn 6.9% of the final sale price if you successfully drive the winning bid.

Your participation in this auction is not just an investment in art, but an investment in our planet. Together, let us seize this opportunity to raise awareness, inspire change, and secure a brighter, greener tomorrow.


This Digital Asset includes:  
The vertical (1080 x 1920) and width (3840 x 2160) animation formats.  
The physical version of this Artwork will be manufactured and tailored specifically for its owner.
